無盡錘
基本屬性:
攻擊力:51
可作為稿子使用:效率為3.0
物品內部具有1個格子，可放置爆裂物作為彈藥

攻擊特效:
對目標施加內部爆破效果，每2秒觸發1次無視防禦的傷害，總共觸發4次，共計造成爆裂物傷害*2的傷害。

每次觸發內部爆破時:
若目標存活，對四周生物造成該次傷害50%的傷害值(計算防禦)。
若目標死亡，對四周生物造成剩餘傷害100%的傷害值(計算防禦)。

若爆裂物為Brightshade Bomb則對暗影生物造成1.1倍的爆破傷害。

Blaze Rip
Damage:51
Pickaxe Efficiency:3.0
Has a slot,which can place explosive items as ammo.(Ex.Gunpower,Slurtle Slime,Brightshade Bomb)

On attack hit:
Apply "Inner Explode" effect,which deal damage(ignore defence) to target periodically.
This effect triggered for every 2 seconds for 4 times.
This effect deal total damage equal to 200% of the ammo damage.

On "Inner Explode" triggerred:
If target survived,deal 50% current damage to nearby enemies.
If target killed,deal 100% remaining damage to nearby enemies.

If ammo in slot is Brightshade Bomb, Inner Explode will deal 1.1 times damage against shadow enemies.
